text: S. M. Mokhlesur Rahman is a Bangladesh Awami League politician and the former Member of Parliament of Satkhira-3. ==Career== Rahman was elected to parliament from Satkhira-3 as a Bangladesh Awami League candidate in 1996. ==References== Category:Awami League politicians Category:Living people Category:7th Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
title: S. M. Mokhlesur Rahman
